{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与乌卓以惑敌之计离开乌府，循精心路线前往秀越山郭府赴宴。途中项少龙追忆舒儿、素女、赵妮及元宗之死，内心悲痛。到达山脚后遇赵墨行者伏击，项少龙以墨子剑法双持飞虹剑与木剑左右开弓，配合飞针暗器大破敌阵，乌卓双连铤亦建功。两人突围后遇荆俊接应，滕翼以夜林箭射杀持火把者及追兵，掩护众人攀索抵达郭府。宴会上郭纵表面殷勤实则暗藏祸心，借敬酒之机挑拨项少龙与赵穆关系。项少龙机智将功劳推给赵穆化解危机。郭纵又企图居中调停项少龙与严平的巨子令之争，被严平拒绝。赵霸携弟子赵致赴宴，赵致主动向项少龙挑战，荆俊挺身而出代师应战。章末政治角力升级，赵穆、郭纵、严平等各方势力暗潮汹涌。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "孙姑爷！前面就是秀越山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这边走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "掉进去哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滕大哥的'夜林箭'名震韩境，连走过的耗子都避不过。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人再敢上来了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们早绑好攀索，又劈开通路，只要沿索而上，可及时到郭府赴宴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们走！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这样大的房子，怎睡得着觉呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "搂个美人儿，还怕睡不着吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大事为重。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫一生都是伴着个打铁炉做人，现在年纪大了，粗重的事交给儿子，闲来只是踩踩穷山野地，找寻穴铁脉，研究一下器械兵刃的型制。对我来说，没有东西比先圣鲁公的手录更珍贵，少龙今天携宝而回，别人或者不知少龙的功劳多大，但老夫却最清楚。来！为我大赵中兴有望干一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "郭纵想害你！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭先生过奖了，末将只是奉大王和侯爷之命尽心办事，所有事均听大王及侯爷指示，末将幸好有点运道，不负所托，我看这一杯应敬的是侯爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫的宴会一向必有歌舞娱宾，但今天巨子肯赏脸来敝府赴宴，所以节目安排上有点改变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看过我的身手才拍掌吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真正要向之喝彩的人是致姑娘，我这些家婢的身手，都是由她一手训练出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "老夫听说少龙与巨子间有点小误会，不若由老夫当个和事老，把事情解决。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭先生这和事老做得太迟了，现在本子和项兵卫的事，只能依从墨门的方式解决。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一位是大王最看重的客卿，一位是大王最宠爱的御前剑士，谁也不愿看到任何一方有失，不若明天由本侯禀奏大王，由他定夺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷的好意心领了，巨子令乃本门至宝，一刻也不能留在外人手上，此事必须立即解决。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项兵卫宫宴与连晋一战，声震赵境，可惜赵某刚到别处考核行馆儿郎的剑技，未能目睹盛况，至今仍耿耿于怀。下面的儿郎均望能见识到项兵卫的绝世剑术，这绝对是切磋性质，希望项兵卫不吝赐教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "请兵卫指点！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "有事弟子服其劳，师父对师父，徒弟对徒弟，便让小子和致姑娘亲热一番。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "小致便领教这位小兄弟的技艺吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    }
  ],
